  "time_ut": 1658631222,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person who jumped out of the fuel line and ran into the police is tamed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It was while trying to get fuel by jumping the queue at the Kurunegala Gonagama petrol station",
        "The police say that a person who went to attack with a sharp weapon was arrested.",
        "The suspect went to a nearby fish shop and tried to attack the police officers there with the manna.",
        "The suspect was injured when one of the officers separated his handcuffs to prevent the assault.",
        "Police officers tamed the suspect and took him to hospital.",
        "The police say that the suspect was arrested on the grounds of obstructing the duty of the police officers, riotous behavior, trying to attack the police officers, etc."
      ],
